components.name: AppComponent
components.templateData: Loading

components.name: ButtonComponent
components.templateData:
<button
  class="atom--button rounded-md uppercase font-semibold box-border"
  (click)="handleButtonClickEvent($event)"
  [ngClass]="[size, type]"
>
  {{ label }}
</button>

components.name: DropdownInputComponent
components.templateData:
<select
  class="
    py-2
    px-3
    border border-darker-grey-color
    rounded-md
    outline-2 outline-secondary-color
    dropdown-select
  "
  (change)="handleChangeOutputEvent(selectedValue.value)"
  [attr.aria-label]="accessibilityLabelName"
  [(ngModel)]="selectedValue.value"
  [attr.id]="inputId"
  [ngClass]="size"
  [attr.required]="isRequired"
>
  <option *ngIf="placeholder !== ''" value="0">{{ placeholder }}</option>
  <option
    *ngFor="let option of options"
    [selected]="option.value"
    [ngValue]="option.value"
  >
    {{ option.display }}
  </option>
</select>

components.name: HeaderComponent
components.templateData: {{ headerTitle }}

components.name: IconComponent
InputLabelComponent
LinkComponent
components.templateData: {{ linkText }} {{ linkText }}

components.name: LogoComponent
ProjectComponent
TextareaInputComponent
components.templateData:
<textarea
  class="
    py-2
    px-3
    border border-darker-grey-color
    rounded-md
    outline-2 outline-secondary-color
  "
  autocomplete="off"
  [(ngModel)]="inputValue"
  [attr.id]="inputId"
  [attr.placeholder]="placeholder"
  [ngClass]="size"
  [attr.required]="isRequired"
  (blur)="handleBlurOutputEvent(inputValue)"
  (focus)="handleFocusOutputEvent(inputValue)"
  (keyup)="handleKeyupOutputEvent(inputValue)"
></textarea>

components.name: TextInputComponent
components.templateData:
<input
  class="
    py-2
    px-3
    border border-darker-grey-color
    rounded-md
    outline-2 outline-secondary-color
  "
  autocomplete="off"
  [(ngModel)]="inputValue"
  [attr.id]="inputId"
  [attr.placeholder]="placeholder"
  [attr.type]="inputType"
  [ngClass]="size"
  [attr.required]="isRequired"
  (blur)="handleBlurOutputEvent(inputValue)"
  (focus)="handleFocusOutputEvent(inputValue)"
  (keyup)="handleKeyupOutputEvent(inputValue)"
/>
